o see a 10F rise in temperature in the room I'm doing sterile work, simply from the heat of the flame.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;I strongly recommend keeping the flame on the outside.&lt;br /&gt;RR</content>\n<name>RogerRabbit</name>\n<next>11323315</next>\n<prev>11320801</prev>\n<first>11319690</first>\n<last>11582391</last>\n<when>1256530922</when>\n<utime>10/26/09 07:22 AM</utime>\n</post>"}